SUMMARY:EDITH ALIBEC: THE VOID
LOCATION:Banshee Labyrinth – Cinema Room\, Edinburgh
DESCRIPTION:Edith has a void. You probably do too - but you know what to do
  with yours and she doesn't. A Romanian clown from slightly outside the hum
 an experience asks the audience what fills it\, then tries everything. Work
 ? Love? Snacks? Playful\, melancholic\, quietly devastating. 'Super energy 
 as both an actor and writer' ★★★★ Scotsman (prev. work)\nMore info:
